text: Malin Maria Åkerman (born 12 May 1978) is a Swedish-Canadian actress. She acted in 27 Dresses in 2008 and in Watchmen in 2009. She also does singing and modeling. She played Kate Harrison in the ABC comedy Trophy Wife. She will appear as Claire Wyden in the 2018 science fiction movie Rampage. Åkerman was born in Stockholm.
